# One Way

Exactly one public path for any outcome. No duplicate APIs, flows, or user-visible alternatives.

- Choose the clearest; remove all others.
- Do not keep the old path when introducing a preferred one — delete it in the same change.
- Internal helpers may be private; public surface must expose only one way.
- At end of change: confirm callers and docs have only one obvious way.